metadata.name: 3706 in Paris by Masnah
metadata.description: The story must be told over and over, as the world learns about this new Internet, cyber security must be an important topic. I believe minting street pixels will lead to great things for our community. Cryptopunk # 3706 AKA Crypto Novo is no clown and will always be remembered for his emphasis on the word UNITY within Community. Street Punks Limited Editions By: Masnah helping us understand the humans behind the pixels
